1
00:01:14,400 --> 00:01:15,200
Stop.

2
00:01:19,360 --> 00:01:20,080
Who are you?

3
00:01:20,080 --> 00:01:21,340
How did you get up here?

4
00:01:57,560 --> 00:01:58,680
How is it going with Dalong?

5
00:01:58,680 --> 00:02:00,540
I couldn't reach him on the phone.

6
00:02:01,120 --> 00:02:02,600
I guess that kid named Shao

7
00:02:04,160 --> 00:02:05,090
is already dead.

8
00:02:29,760 --> 00:02:31,960
Someone is making trouble in the corridor.

9
00:02:31,960 --> 00:02:33,200
That kid is dead.

10
00:02:33,880 --> 00:02:35,720
But what if he has the USB drive?

11
00:02:40,400 --> 00:02:41,200
It's fine.

12
00:02:43,200 --> 00:02:45,200
He wouldn't die before giving it up.

13
00:02:45,480 --> 00:02:47,040
Even if he doesn't have it,

14
00:02:48,000 --> 00:02:49,860
it must be with those three girls.

15
00:02:50,360 --> 00:02:52,120
They won't be able to hold out.

16
00:03:04,320 --> 00:03:05,440
I mean just in case.

17
00:03:06,640 --> 00:03:09,200
What if the USB drive is with Shao?

18
00:03:09,200 --> 00:03:10,480
Once he's dead,

19
00:03:11,240 --> 00:03:13,360
and the contents are leaked...

20
00:03:14,160 --> 00:03:15,640
So what if it gets out?

21
00:03:16,920 --> 00:03:19,120
The video in it has nothing to do with me.

22
00:03:21,320 --> 00:03:23,320
At worst, those guys will go to jail.

23
00:03:24,520 --> 00:03:26,760
We spent so much money and energy

24
00:03:27,680 --> 00:03:30,640
building that network. It would be gone.

25
00:03:31,560 --> 00:03:33,280
I have plenty of money.

26
00:03:34,600 --> 00:03:35,840
As long as I'm around,

27
00:03:38,040 --> 00:03:40,640
Tangzhou City will always belong to the Dings.

28
00:03:59,120 --> 00:04:00,120
Principal Zhang.

29
00:04:00,360 --> 00:04:02,960
Where is the video of their school's art performance?

30
00:04:02,960 --> 00:04:04,820
On the TV in the upstairs bedroom.

31
00:05:16,360 --> 00:05:18,290
It seems you're not only stubborn,

32
00:05:18,960 --> 00:05:20,280
but also tough to kill.

33
00:05:23,840 --> 00:05:26,040
But you're not very smart

34
00:05:28,480 --> 00:05:30,210
to deliver yourself to my door.

35
00:05:30,720 --> 00:05:33,120
I was going to thank you for the compliment,

36
00:05:33,200 --> 00:05:35,240
but you said I'm not very smart.

37
00:05:36,120 --> 00:05:39,640
My brain might be my biggest advantage over you.

38
00:06:04,800 --> 00:06:06,460
You are quite well-prepared.

39
00:06:07,880 --> 00:06:10,440
But in the face of absolute power,

40
00:06:11,560 --> 00:06:15,360
cleverness can only give you the upper hand for a moment.

41
00:06:17,000 --> 00:06:18,040
In the end,

42
00:06:19,040 --> 00:06:21,200
it depends on whose fist is harder.

43
00:07:42,840 --> 00:07:44,040
How did you get in?

44
00:07:46,320 --> 00:07:47,760
Does that matter now?

45
00:07:48,680 --> 00:07:49,480
Him.

46
00:07:50,200 --> 00:07:51,320
Did you kill him?

47
00:07:52,040 --> 00:07:52,840
Yes.

48
00:07:54,680 --> 00:07:57,159
And you are next.

49
00:08:07,080 --> 00:08:07,880
Tell me.

50
00:08:10,600 --> 00:08:12,200
What will it take to let me go?

51
00:08:12,280 --> 00:08:14,410
Money, women, status. Take your pick.

52
00:08:16,240 --> 00:08:18,760
Don't you want to go back to the police department?

53
00:08:18,760 --> 00:08:19,560
Rest assured.

54
00:08:20,280 --> 00:08:21,610
I can help you with that.

55
00:08:23,720 --> 00:08:25,720
I have no interest in any of that.

56
00:08:27,080 --> 00:08:28,480
If you want to live,

57
00:08:29,120 --> 00:08:32,720
hand over the videos of you abusing women.

58
00:08:33,120 --> 00:08:33,799
No.

59
00:08:35,679 --> 00:08:37,000
I can't give you that.

60
00:08:38,880 --> 00:08:39,840
Other than that,

61
00:08:40,799 --> 00:08:43,120
I can satisfy any of your demands.

62
00:08:46,000 --> 00:08:47,240
That is all I want.

63
00:08:57,160 --> 00:08:58,620
I really can't figure out.

64
00:08:58,840 --> 00:09:01,000
Why must you have it?

65
00:09:01,000 --> 00:09:02,320
Taking it from me

66
00:09:02,840 --> 00:09:04,800
is no different from killing me.

67
00:09:06,800 --> 00:09:08,930
We have no grudges against each other.

68
00:09:09,680 --> 00:09:12,080
What good is bringing me down to you?

69
00:09:12,560 --> 00:09:14,480
Is it just for those three girls?

70
00:09:14,480 --> 00:09:15,440
Not entirely.

71
00:09:16,280 --> 00:09:18,080
I did promise those three girls

72
00:09:18,080 --> 00:09:19,480
to get their videos back.

73
00:09:20,640 --> 00:09:22,160
So I must keep my word.

74
00:09:23,600 --> 00:09:24,640
Besides,

75
00:09:24,640 --> 00:09:26,360
you made my life miserable.

76
00:09:27,880 --> 00:09:29,410
Shouldn't I get my revenge?

77
00:09:32,960 --> 00:09:34,960
Then there is nothing to talk about.

78
00:09:38,800 --> 00:09:39,440
Fine.

79
00:09:42,400 --> 00:09:43,960
Then kill me.

80
00:09:45,200 --> 00:09:46,160
Okay.

81
00:09:52,320 --> 00:09:54,640
This is a Type 64 pistol.

82
00:09:54,640 --> 00:09:55,840
It has seven bullets.

83
00:09:56,440 --> 00:09:57,440
Two went to the assassins

84
00:09:57,440 --> 00:09:59,640
you sent after me and Jessica.

85
00:10:00,400 --> 00:10:01,640
Two went to him.

86
00:10:02,360 --> 00:10:03,800
The remaining three,

87
00:10:04,320 --> 00:10:06,040
I saved all for you.

88
00:10:07,600 --> 00:10:10,040
I might have to break my promise to those girls.

89
00:10:10,040 --> 00:10:10,920
But...

90
00:10:11,200 --> 00:10:12,200
Killing you

91
00:10:12,720 --> 00:10:14,380
will be much more satisfying.

92
00:10:32,520 --> 00:10:36,200
You know I've done so many things you consider evil,

93
00:10:36,200 --> 00:10:38,040
yet still stand strong.

94
00:10:38,040 --> 00:10:39,280
Do you know why?

95
00:10:40,680 --> 00:10:42,800
Because I'm lucky enough.

96
00:10:44,160 --> 00:10:45,820
And this time is no exception.

97
00:11:22,400 --> 00:11:23,530
Hello, Attorney An.

98
00:11:25,520 --> 00:11:27,380
You called at just the right time.

99
00:11:28,640 --> 00:11:31,640
I happen to have a matter I need you to handle for me.

100
00:11:33,360 --> 00:11:35,090
Is it about you killing Shao Yu?

101
00:11:37,840 --> 00:11:38,880
How did you know?

102
00:11:39,520 --> 00:11:41,240
You fell into Shao Yu's trap.

103
00:11:53,920 --> 00:11:56,050
He deliberately let you shoot him dead

104
00:11:56,160 --> 00:11:59,240
to use his death as evidence of your murder.

105
00:12:00,000 --> 00:12:02,060
That way, even without those videos,

106
00:12:02,240 --> 00:12:05,240
this footage plus the contents of the flash drive

107
00:12:05,240 --> 00:12:06,720
is enough to convict you.

108
00:12:50,240 --> 00:12:51,040
Attorney An.

109
00:12:53,280 --> 00:12:54,400
You know

110
00:12:55,600 --> 00:12:57,280
that videos can be edited.

111
00:12:59,160 --> 00:13:01,360
Besides, he shot me first.

112
00:13:02,160 --> 00:13:03,960
His fingerprints are on the gun.

113
00:13:05,280 --> 00:13:07,210
I was just acting in self-defense.

114
00:13:08,840 --> 00:13:10,440
Then go check his fingers.

115
00:13:35,240 --> 00:13:37,680
When did you take his side?

116
00:13:41,320 --> 00:13:43,680
As for getting any other help from me,

117
00:13:44,440 --> 00:13:46,440
you'll need to offer more leverage.

118
00:13:52,680 --> 00:13:53,200
Okay.

119
00:13:53,600 --> 00:13:54,240
Got it.

120
00:14:04,680 --> 00:14:06,740
You are not that kind of person at all.

121
00:14:12,200 --> 00:14:14,640
You only colluded with them to survive.

122
00:14:15,760 --> 00:14:16,920
What you just said

123
00:14:17,600 --> 00:14:19,200
was merely an excuse

124
00:14:19,520 --> 00:14:21,000
to convince yourself.

125
00:14:22,000 --> 00:14:23,640
You are not like them.

126
00:14:26,000 --> 00:14:27,130
Your inner goodness

127
00:14:29,080 --> 00:14:32,840
has just been blinded by vanity and weakness.

128
00:14:33,800 --> 00:14:35,840
The so-called extreme egoist

129
00:14:36,120 --> 00:14:36,850
is just a mask

130
00:14:38,200 --> 00:14:39,680
to disguise yourself.

131
00:14:51,720 --> 00:14:53,240
Now here is a chance

132
00:14:53,760 --> 00:14:56,240
for you to accept your true self.

133
00:14:57,360 --> 00:14:59,160
I will give you all the data

134
00:14:59,160 --> 00:15:02,320
on the grey market transactions we worked so hard

135
00:15:03,040 --> 00:15:04,100
to get and decrypt.

136
00:15:04,920 --> 00:15:08,320
If you still think you're the same kind of person as Ding Tian,

137
00:15:08,720 --> 00:15:10,240
you can give it back to him.

138
00:15:11,640 --> 00:15:13,800
Even if all our hard work is in vain,

139
00:15:14,040 --> 00:15:15,280
and it might cost

140
00:15:16,040 --> 00:15:17,500
a few more lives in the end.

141
00:15:18,680 --> 00:15:20,520
But I trust my own judgment.

142
00:15:21,720 --> 00:15:23,050
I am not wrong about you.

143
00:15:24,600 --> 00:15:27,130
You will definitely make a different choice.

144
00:15:44,320 --> 00:15:45,120
Wait a minute.

145
00:15:54,240 --> 00:15:55,480
What is your plan?

146
00:16:00,960 --> 00:16:02,200
Hello, Mr. An.

147
00:16:03,160 --> 00:16:05,160
I have things to do.

148
00:16:05,320 --> 00:16:06,080
I know.

149
00:16:21,680 --> 00:16:22,600
No wonder

150
00:16:24,240 --> 00:16:26,360
he could come directly to this floor.

151
00:16:27,400 --> 00:16:29,160
You gave him the card.

152
00:16:29,920 --> 00:16:30,840
Mr. An,

153
00:16:32,560 --> 00:16:35,040
I've treated you well all along, haven't I?

154
00:16:37,440 --> 00:16:39,200
Just tell me what you want.

155
00:16:40,000 --> 00:16:41,460
Now it's a deal between us.

156
00:16:42,120 --> 00:16:45,360
Actually, I've never thought about taking revenge on you.

157
00:16:45,360 --> 00:16:46,720
My only request

158
00:16:48,520 --> 00:16:51,240
is that you return the video of me.

159
00:16:53,000 --> 00:16:54,280
Which video?

160
00:16:55,600 --> 00:16:56,720
You know.

161
00:16:58,120 --> 00:16:59,240
Is it that simple?

162
00:17:01,400 --> 00:17:02,680
I'm not like them.

163
00:17:03,080 --> 00:17:05,960
Actually, I am an extreme egoist.

164
00:17:06,720 --> 00:17:07,880
More realistic,

165
00:17:08,240 --> 00:17:10,240
and I cherish everything I have now.

166
00:17:10,800 --> 00:17:14,000
So I don't want the stain on my life

167
00:17:14,000 --> 00:17:16,000
to run the risk of being discovered.

168
00:17:16,760 --> 00:17:18,160
I'll give you half an hour

169
00:17:18,560 --> 00:17:19,890
to bring the video here.

170
00:17:20,200 --> 00:17:22,000
Otherwise, I'll send this recording

171
00:17:22,000 --> 00:17:22,960
to the police.

172
00:19:13,240 --> 00:19:13,320
Lighting Team.
